snippet.title: I Am Future - Official Early Access Release Date Trailer | Publisher Spotlight Showcase 2023
snippet.description: I Am Future is coming to Steam Early Access on August 8, 2023 and a demo is available now. Sing along to the catchy tune while getting a look at this cozy post-apocalypse world in this trailer for I Am Future. In Am Future, you're alone on a skyscraper roof in a flooded city. Build, craft, farm, fish, cook - with a view. Or go on exploration, meet other survivors, and uncover the truth about the fall of humanity.
